caption.p: Impact of HPV-16/18 vaccination on recurrence of HPV infections and cervical lesions after excision treatment. HPV: human papillomavirus; HR-HPV: high-risk human papillomavirus; LR-HPV: low-risk human papillomavirus; LSIL+:low-grade squamous intraepithelial lesion or worse; HSIL+: high-grade squamous intraepithelial lesion or worse; CI: confidence interval; NA: not available
